## Checkpoint: The Full Review

You asked AI to build a landing page for a fitness studio. It gave you the following code. Your job is to review it — find the structural issues, visual bugs, JavaScript errors, and accessibility problems — and then write the prompts to fix them.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FitStudio</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 20px; }
    .nav-links a { color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; }

    .hero {
      background-color: #16213e;
      color: #16213e;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 24px; }

    .cta-btn {
      background-color: #e94560;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .classes {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .classes h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .class-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .class-card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .class-card img { width: 100%; }
    .class-card h3 { padding: 16px 16px 8px; }
    .class-card p { padding: 0 16px 16px; color: #666; }

    .footer {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .class-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="nav">
    <h1>FitStudio</h1>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#classes">Classes</a></li>
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="menu-toggle" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</div>
  </div>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Transform Your Body</h1>
    <p>Join our expert-led classes and start your fitness journey today.</p>
    <div class="cta-btn" onclick="signup()">Start Free Trial</div>
  </section>

  <section class="classes" id="classes">
    <h2>Our Classes</h2>
    <div class="class-grid">
      <div class="class-card">
        <img src="yoga.jpg">
        <h3>Yoga Flow</h3>
        <p>Find your balance with our relaxing yoga sessions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="class-card">
        <img src="hiit.jpg">
        <h3>HIIT Blast</h3>
        <p>High intensity intervals to torch calories fast.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="class-card">
        <img src="spin.jpg">
        <h3>Spin Cycle</h3>
        <p>Ride to the beat in our energizing spin classes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>© 2024 FitStudio. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleMenu() {
      document.querySelector('.nav-list').classList.toggle('active');
    }

    function signup() {
      alert('Signing up!');
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
```

